Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家站在同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么美丽的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的  我好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说  这结果很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好感动
